Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 168
By: Swami Ramdas
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Volition, Obedience and Conformity=Volition
  - 501
---
(The) inner voice speaks in the devotee when he has surrendered up his
body, mind and soul into the keeping of the Divine who dwells within
him.
